ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseM3-name = standard M3 pattern marine armor set
ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseM3-desc = A case containing standard M3 pattern marine armor, an M10 helmet, and attachable armor pieces.
ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseM3Smooth-name = smooth M3 pattern marine armor set
ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseM3Smooth-desc = A case containing smooth M3 pattern marine armor, an M10 helmet, and attachable armor pieces.
ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseM3Ridged-name = ridged M3 pattern marine armor set
ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseM3Ridged-desc = A case containing ridged M3 pattern marine armor, an M10 helmet, and attachable armor pieces.
ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseB12-name = B12 pattern marine armor set
ent-RMCPVEArmorCaseB12-desc = A case containing B12 pattern marine armor, an M10 helmet, and attachable armor pieces.
